<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>External documentation</b></p><p>To open your browser with the documentation page for the element at the caret, press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:ExternalJavaDoc;</span> or select <span class="control">Tools | Web Browsers and Preview</span> from the main menu.</p><p>Ensure that you set a default browser in the settings. To check the default browser, open settings by pressing <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:ShowSettings;</span> and navigate to <span class="shortcut">Tools | Web Browsers and Preview</span>.</p></body></html>